{"tid":632023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍晒新「航母殺手」　 可載核覆蓋關島","createTime":"2018-04-17T04:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T14:50:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0eb222e1125115207c32609c78f1e24273673f","tid":632023,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180417/20363882?_ga=2.141215794.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363882%3F_ga%3D2.141215794.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=Dbc4MV86%2FLTMa%2BN%2BR%2BEI%2BqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=442d86f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363882%3F_ga%3D2.141215794.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=6d9f731c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180417/20363882?_ga=2.141215794.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n解放軍晒新「航母殺手」　<br />\n可載核覆蓋關島<br />\n<br />\n3.9K<br />\n兩岸要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/1523895890_7185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F1523895890_7185.jpg&h=ba692858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美軍事角力逐步升溫，央視播出片段，指解放軍已正式列裝一款新型導彈（圖），內媒推測新裝備是新一代中遠程彈道導彈「東風26」，能搭載核彈頭或常規彈頭，可快速作核反擊，射程涵蓋關島美軍基地。新導彈裝列標誌解放軍提升火箭軍的戰略能力。<br />\n<br />\n殲10C加入戰鬥值班<br />\n<br />\n央視《新聞聯播》昨播出片段，指火箭軍新型導彈武器加入戰鬥序列，片中提到「它核常兼備，可對陸上重要目標和海上大中型艦船進行中遠程精確打擊」，新浪軍事點明新型導彈是有「航母殺手」稱號的「東風26」。「東風26」在2015年首次亮相，最大射程3,000至4,000公里，覆蓋關島，擁有打擊第二島鏈固定目標和大型艦艇等能力。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍亦宣佈，去年7月首次亮相的殲10C戰機，昨開始負起戰鬥值班任務，它是中國自主研發的第三代超音速多用途戰機，配備航電系統及多型先進機載武器，具備中近距制空和對地、對海精確打擊能力，據報戰機部署在西藏，應對印度的威脅。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，解放軍明天將在福建獅靶場沿海舉行實彈軍事演習，國台辦主任劉結一表示，軍演是捍衞祖國主權和領土完整的行動。<br />\n<br />\n中新網/中時電子報"},{"pid":"178bca37b941f5a6a67be3758350c46718dc616e","tid":632023,"uid":169555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"GPS? 精準度如何？"},{"pid":"c18e6d950d882d7cd7a9d1505addd181a9d2b9af","tid":632023,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GPS? 精準度如何？</blockquote><br />\n強國用北斗導航系統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692495e28d38aed491da368835e61352a8292557","tid":632023,"uid":72457,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"打完隻航母 中國會變歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a45ab315d6c005fa07b34796bb6ac6b42a91983","tid":632023,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dfe1125808ff61ea097cd8dad66b5449fd78f43","tid":632023,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:36:10.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F